{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">If you're reading this you might be on the fence as to whether to buy the game with your hard earned $ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">I dont think anything you read here will push you over the edge. Check the reviews online, watch some videos you'll see we have a solid rep.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">If you like puzzle games then take the plunge. If you dont like you can always refund!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">If you have a partner/friend/relative/child you can also play with them and have a great time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u26a0\u26a0\u26a0 Play online with friends using Steam's Remote Play Together! \u26a0\u26a0\u26a0 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">But the game is great solo. You just use both sides of your brain at once!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">OK back to the usual description. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Death Squared</strong> is a cooperative puzzle game for 1, 2 or 4 players, best enjoyed with loved ones who don't mind a little arguing for the greater good.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Prove your teamwork skills in <strong>Death Squared</strong> as you solve puzzles together or die trying! Each player needs to guide a robot to a colour-coded goal, but the path is beset with deadly traps and hazards. Teams of players will need close observation and communication to keep each other alive and discover a solution together.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Complete the main campaign with one or two players, then take a group into four-player Party Mode for the ultimate teamwork trial! For those that can't get enough, head to the 'Vault' to find extra experiments recommended only for the brave.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><i>Features:</i></u></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">a micro-journey of: surprise &gt; discovery &gt; mastery &gt; success</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Full voice acting by Ricepirate</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">80x puzzling levels in the Story levels</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">40x 4 Player Party levels</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">45x Vault Levels (too hard for the main game)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/471810/extras/Bots-Low-B.png?t=1733198667\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/471810/extras/PaxWestIMB.png?t=1733198667\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/471810/extras/PaxEastIMB.png?t=1733198667\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/471810/extras/PaxAuSC.png?t=1733198667\" /></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Did the thing","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/471810/28f3a5a82e90e4ca6aa5710c5fc4546dac37d78c.jpg"},{"name":"Sir Die A Lot","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/471810/278463354fdbd79fc76df96d4ea9982b7373d940.jpg"},{"name":"Die 100 times","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/471810/93eea0ae06a6ceb17d3a984d34380249b6d98efb.jpg"},{"name":"Die Heaps","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/471810/cb71df58755ff708f82fe294f406e126897011ed.jpg"},{"name":"Did many things","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/471810/da76d4a2a0391a44b46b5996ffd9f72543897b89.jpg"},{"name":"Did a lot of things","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity